{"name":"Detective","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"lawful good","hitDice":"9","armorName":"breastplate","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (scale mail)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"91 (14d8 + 28)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"11","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"14","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"13","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"4 (1,100 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The city watch captain can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The city watch captain regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the city watch captain can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the city watch captain can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The city watch captain can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the city watch captain's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the city watch captain's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the city watch captain dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes one rapier attacks and one dagger attack."},{"name":"Rapier","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1d8] piercing damage."},{"name":"Dagger","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 [DEX 1d4] piercing damage."},{"name":"Light Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1d8] piercing damage."},{"name":"Watch Whistle","desc":"The [MON] blows a loud whistle, summoning [1d8+1] Harport City Watch people in [1d4] rounds."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Tactical Insight (2/day)","desc":"The [MON] makes a contested insight check against the target's deception. On a success, the [MON] and it's allies get advantage on the creature for 1 round."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}